data.description: Introducing 1222 Peachtree St in the sought-after Miramar neighborhood! This adorable bungalow effortlessly combines historic charm with modern comfort, offering a cozy living experience in a prime location. Every inch of this home has been lovingly restored and upgraded, ensuring a perfect touch of classic charm. Original architectural details, including hardwood floors and exposed brick, add character and warmth to the space. The home features two spacious bedrooms and a versatile flex room, perfect for your home office or play room. The main bathroom has been totally updated. The heart of the home is the stunning kitchen. It's a chef's paradise with all new appliances, ample counter space, and modern cabinetry. The laundry area, situated just off the kitchen, offers not only the convenience of in-house laundry but also plenty of storage space and a half bath, which is perfect for guests! You'll have peace of mind with a brand new roof, AC system, new windows, and many more updates. Don't just visit, make this HOME!
